<script>
  import globalVariable from "../src/components/global/GlobalVariable.vue"
  
  export default {
    methods : {
      /**
       * 将全局变量中的user赋值
       * @param user 用于赋值的用户变量
       */
      setGlobalUser(user) {
        globalVariable.user.userName = user.userName
        globalVariable.user.userId = user.userId
        globalVariable.user.userPassword = user.userPassword
        globalVariable.user.userIdentity = user.userIdentity
      }
    }

  }
</script>
